testsuite.name: com.kaiqkt.authentication.unit.domain.services.SessionServiceTest

testcase.name: given a id, refresh token and a user should create a session()
given a id and a user id when session does not exist should throw a domain exception()
given a session id when session exist should return it()
given a session id when session not exist should return null()
given a refresh token when not exist a session should thrown a exception()
given a refresh token when exist a session should return successfully()
given a id and a user id when session exist should revoke successfully()
